- **TimeBack Design System Colors:**
  - **Primary Color**: `timeback-primary` (#0f33bb) - Dark blue for text and primary elements
  - **Background Color**: `timeback-bg` (#1abeff) - Light blue for backgrounds and highlights
  - **White**: `white` (#ffffff) - Clean backgrounds and contrast elements
  - **ALL text must use the `font-cal` font family**

- **Mandatory Typography:**
  - **EVERY text element MUST include `font-cal`**
  - Apply to: headings (h1-h6), paragraphs, buttons, labels, all text content
  - Example: `className="font-cal text-timeback-primary"`

- **Core Color Mappings (Replace ALL instances):**

  ```typescript
  // ✅ TEXT COLORS - Use timeback-primary for ALL text
  text-blue-600 → text-timeback-primary
  text-blue-700 → text-timeback-primary  
  text-blue-800 → text-timeback-primary
  text-gray-900 → text-timeback-primary
  text-gray-800 → text-timeback-primary
  text-gray-700 → text-timeback-primary
  text-gray-600 → text-timeback-primary
  text-gray-500 → text-timeback-primary
  text-green-600 → text-timeback-primary
  text-green-700 → text-timeback-primary
  text-red-600 → text-timeback-primary
  text-red-700 → text-timeback-primary

  // ✅ BACKGROUND COLORS - Use timeback-bg for highlights
  bg-blue-50 → bg-timeback-bg
  bg-blue-100 → bg-timeback-bg
  bg-gray-50 → bg-timeback-bg
  bg-gray-100 → bg-timeback-bg
  bg-green-50 → bg-timeback-bg
  bg-green-100 → bg-timeback-bg
  bg-red-50 → bg-timeback-bg
  bg-white → bg-white (keep unchanged)

  // ✅ BORDER COLORS - Use timeback-primary for all borders
  border-blue-200 → border-timeback-primary
  border-blue-600 → border-timeback-primary
  border-gray-200 → border-timeback-primary
  border-gray-300 → border-timeback-primary
  border-green-600 → border-timeback-primary
  border-red-600 → border-timeback-primary

  // ✅ HOVER STATES
  hover:text-blue-600 → hover:text-timeback-primary
  hover:text-blue-700 → hover:text-timeback-primary
  hover:bg-blue-50 → hover:bg-timeback-bg
  hover:bg-blue-100 → hover:bg-timeback-bg
  hover:bg-gray-50 → hover:bg-timeback-bg
  hover:border-blue-600 → hover:border-timeback-primary
  ```

- **Enhanced Design System Elements:**

  ```typescript
  // ✅ BORDER RADIUS UPGRADES
  rounded-lg → rounded-xl
  rounded-md → rounded-xl

  // ✅ SHADOW UPGRADES  
  shadow-md → shadow-lg
  shadow-lg → shadow-xl
  shadow-xl → shadow-2xl

  // ✅ GRADIENT REPLACEMENTS
  bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 to-blue-100 → bg-gradient-to-br from-timeback-bg to-white
  bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-purple-600 → bg-gradient-to-r from-timeback-primary to-timeback-primary
  ```

- **TimeBack Color Values (tailwind.config.js):**
  ```javascript
  timeback: {
    bg: '#1abeff',      // Light blue background
    primary: '#0f33bb', // Dark blue for text/elements  
    white: '#ffffff'    // White for accents
  }
  ```

- **Component Implementation Examples:**

  ```typescript
  // ✅ CORRECT TimeBack Implementation
  className="font-cal bg-timeback-bg text-timeback-primary border-timeback-primary rounded-xl shadow-lg"
  className="font-cal text-timeback-primary hover:text-timeback-primary"
  className="font-cal bg-white border-timeback-primary rounded-xl"
  
  // ❌ FORBIDDEN - Old color system
  className="bg-blue-50 text-blue-600"       // Must use timeback colors
  className="text-gray-500"                  // Must use timeback-primary
  className="border-gray-200 rounded-lg"     // Must use timeback-primary and rounded-xl
  ```

